        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="好工具周刊（第-3-期）"><a href="#好工具周刊（第-3-期）" class="headerlink" title="好工具周刊（第 3 期）"></a>好工具周刊（第 3 期）</h1><p>发现并分享有趣，有创意，免费，好用的工具，周五发布。由<a href="https://blog.hutaowife.com/">YzMzxl</a>创作。</p><hr><h2 id="🌈-在线工具"><a href="#🌈-在线工具" class="headerlink" title="🌈 在线工具"></a>🌈 在线工具</h2><hr><h3 id="TinySnap"><a href="#TinySnap" class="headerlink" title="TinySnap"></a><a href="https://tinysnap.app/zh-cn/">TinySnap</a></h3><blockquote><p>本文网页截图均使用此插件</p></blockquote><p>TinySnap 是一款浏览器截图扩展插件，它最主要的功能就是截图和美化。不同于传统的截图方式，使用 TinySnap 可以对你所截的的图片进行简单设计，从而美化展示效果，十分适合内容生产者、营销人员以及运营人员等。TinySnap 也支持多种截图方式，例如可见区域截图、选定区域截图或者对整个页面进行长截图，甚至你还可以上传本地图像进行美化处理！目前扩展插件支持 Chrome 浏览器和 Edge 浏览器，并且 99% 的功能对用户免费开放。</p><p>链接: <a href="https://tinysnap.app/zh-cn/">https://tinysnap.app/</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303142512076.png" alt="image-20230303142512076"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303142714199.png" alt="image-20230303142714199"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303142906098.png" alt="image-20230303142906098"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303142841481.png" alt="image-20230303142841481"></p><h3 id="Internxt-Send"><a href="#Internxt-Send" class="headerlink" title="Internxt Send"></a><a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/send.internxt.com/">Internxt Send</a></h3><p>免费的在线加密传输文件、分享文件的工具，文件最大支持 5GB。</p><p>链接: <a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/send.internxt.com/">https://send.internxt.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303143252536.png" alt="image-20230303143252536"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303143337354.png" alt="image-20230303143337354"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303143554888.png" alt="image-20230303143554888"></p><h3 id="iHateRegex"><a href="#iHateRegex" class="headerlink" title="iHateRegex"></a><a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/ihateregex.io/">iHateRegex</a></h3><p>为不熟悉正则表达式的开发者准备的 Cheat Sheet。</p><p>链接: <a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/ihateregex.io/">https://ihateregex.io/</a></p><p>源码: <a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/github.com/geongeorge/i-hate-regex">https://github.com/geongeorge/i-hate-regex</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303143757899.png" alt="image-20230303143757899"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303143814745.png" alt="image-20230303143814745"></p><h3 id="haikei"><a href="#haikei" class="headerlink" title="haikei"></a><a href="https://app.haikei.app/">haikei</a></h3><p>自定义生成自己的专属背景。</p><p>链接: <a href="https://app.haikei.app/">https://app.haikei.app</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303144122634.png" alt="image-20230303144122634"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303144200112.png" alt="image-20230303144200112"></p><h3 id="RegexLearn"><a href="#RegexLearn" class="headerlink" title="RegexLearn"></a><a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/regexlearn.com/zh-cn">RegexLearn</a></h3><p>一个轻松学习、练习、测试正则表达式的工具。希望大家都能熟练使用正则表达式，正则表达式其实没有那么难。</p><p>链接: <a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/regexlearn.com/zh-cn">https://regexlearn.com/zh-cn</a></p><p>源码: <a href="https://links.bestxtools.com/github.com/aykutkardas/regexlearn.com">https://github.com/aykutkardas/regexlearn.com</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303144454079.png" alt="image-20230303144454079"></p><h3 id="qrbtf"><a href="#qrbtf" class="headerlink" title="qrbtf"></a><a href="https://qrbtf.com/">qrbtf</a></h3><p>一款二维码美化工具，支持多种格式保存</p><p>链接: <a href="https://qrbtf.com/">https://qrbtf.com</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.hutaowife.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YzMzxl/Typora-img/master/img/image-20230303144658374.png" alt="image-20230303144658374"></p><hr><h2 id="🌈-工具推荐"><a href="#🌈-工具推荐" class="headerlink" title="🌈 工具推荐"></a>🌈 工具推荐</h2><p>以上，便是本期全部内容。本期最喜欢的工具是哪一个，请在评论区留言。感谢你阅读到这里，下期见！<br>欢迎投稿自己觉得实用工具<br>要求：</p><ul><li>在线工具</li><li>免费</li><li>无需注册</li></ul><p>欢迎交流，投稿，订阅。</p><hr><p><a href="https://blog.hutaowife.com/posts/30544.html">上一期内容</a> | <a href="">下一期内容</a> | <a href="https://blog.hutaowife.com/categories/%E5%A5%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%91%A8%E5%88%8A">往期内容</a> | <a href="https://blog.hutaowife.com/atom.xml">RSS 订阅</a></p><hr>]]></content>
      
      
